title: Disclosure, Live From The 2013 Mt. Oasis Festival
description: It's been a pretty big year for Brit producers (and brothers) Guy and Howard Lawrence. The electronic duo, better known as Disclosure, released their debut album, Settle, to great fanfare, and have been selling out venues across America. This set was recorded live in Asheville, NC on Oct. 27, 2013. F Four You When A Fire Starts You & Me White Noise Voices What's In Your Head Confess To Me Running (Disclosure Remix) Help Me Lose My Mind Latch
